MARY PARISH AND THE SURROUNDING AREA. CONSTRUCTION AND OPERATION OF THE PARK WERE PROVIDED FOR IN THE WILLS OF KEMPER AND LEILA WILLIAMS AND ACCOMPLISHED THROUGH AN ACT OF DONATION ON JULY 26, 1978.
